text: E36 may refer to: * Nimzo-Indian Defence, Encyclopaedia of Chess Openings code * The BMW E36 automobile platform * The European route E36 connecting Berlin to Bolesławiec * The Federal Aviation Administration airport code of Georgetown Airport (California) * Cryotech E36, a Potassium acetate based runway deicer * Penang Bridge, route E36 in Malaysia
title: E36
